<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><presentation>v1 v2 v3 v4 v5 v6 </presentation>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Holiness is Your life in me
 Making me clean through Your blood
 Holiness is Your fire in me
 Purging my heart like a flood

[V2]
 Hellighet er Ditt Liv i meg
 Renser meg ren i Ditt Blod
 Hellighet er Din Ild i meg
 Lutrer min sjel som en flod

[V3]
 I know You are
 Perfect in holiness
 Your life in me
 Setting me free
 Making me holy

[V4]
 Jeg vet Du er
 Fullkommen, Hellig, Ren
 Ditt Liv i meg
 Setter meg fri
 Du gjør meg Hellig

[V5]
 Only the blood of Jesus
 Takes away all my sin
 Only the life of Jesus
 Renews me from within
 Your blood is enough
 Your mercy complete
 Your work of atonement
 Paid for my debts
 Making me holy

[V6]
 Bare Ditt Blod O Jesus
 Renser bort all min synd
 Bare Ditt Liv O Jesus
 Fornyer mitt sinn
 Ditt Blod Det er nok
 Din Nåde fullkommen
 Ditt Verk av Forsoning
 betalte min skyld
 Du gjør meg hellig
 Bare Ditt Blod O Jesus</lyrics>
<title>Bare ditt blod</title>
</song>